Ruotsi on jo aiemmin sanonut osallistuvansa harjoitukseen, ja Niinistö oli kertonut suunnitelmasta myös muille Helsingissä vierailleille kollegoilleen. 
Suomi ei ole mitään pyytämässä mistään. 
Niinistö kertoi keskustelujen päätteeksi amerikkalaiskollegansa ymmärtävän hyvin Suomen nykyistä puolustuspoliittista linjaa, jossa yhtyvät sotilaallinen liittoutumattomuus ja tiivis yhteistyö Naton ja muiden kumppaneiden kanssa. 
– Ministeri Mattis kertoi, että Yhdysvallat arvostaa tätä Suomen linjaa ja ymmärtää sen, ettei Suomen kansa ole Natoon liittymässä, Niinistö sanoi. 
Erityisiä lupauksia Suomen auttamisesta tai rinnalla seisomisesta Niinistö ei vaikuttanut alkuviikon ministeritapaamisista odottaneen tai kaivanneen. 
– Suomi ei ole mitään pyytämässä mistään. Me valmistaudumme puolustamaan omaa valtioaluettamme yksin, mutta jos saamme apua kumppanimailta, niin aina parempi. Yritämme tehdä tasavallan presidentin sanoin itsestämme houkuttelevan kumppanin, Niinistö muotoili. 
– Sitten jos rähinä alkaa, kyllä niitä liittokuntia sitten syntyy, on sotilaallisesti liittoutunut sitä ennen tai ei. 
Ei tässä mitään uutta liittokuntaa olla rakentamassa. 
Tiistaina pidettiin myös lajissaan ensimmäinen Yhdysvaltain, Ruotsin ja Suomen kolmenvälinen puolustusministeritapaaminen. Ruotsin Peter Hultqvistin mukaan kokous tällä tasolla on tärkeä turvallisuuspoliittinen viesti ulospäin. 
– Se on vahva todiste siitä, että Yhdysvallat on kiinnostunut meidän alueestamme Euroopassa, Hultqvist sanoi STT:lle. 
Hänen mukaansa Suomen ja Ruotsin tiivis yhteistyö keskenään sekä samanlaiset yhteistyöjärjestelyt Yhdysvaltain kanssa ovat luonnollinen pohja kolmenvälisille tapaamisille. 
Ministeri Niinistö puolestaan korosti, ettei kolmenvälinen yhteydenpito korvaa vaan täydentää kahdenvälisiä suhteita. 
– Ei tässä mitään uutta liittokuntaa olla rakentamassa, hän toppuutteli. 
Joka tapauksessa uusi ministeritapaaminen on suunnitteilla jo ensi keväälle. Niinistön mukaan ainakin hybridiuhat ja niiden torjuminen ovat tuolloin varma puheenaihe. 
Suomeen vastikään perustettu hybridiosaamiskeskus on saanut Niinistön mukaan muutenkin huomiota ja kiinnostusta osakseen lähes joka käänteessä. 
– Toivottavasti sille on sitten katettakin, sen eteen täytyy tehdä töitä. Kovat paineethan tämä asettaa keskuksen työntekijöille ja verkoston osallistujille, että sieltä sitten todella saadaan konkreettista hyötyä. 
STT–NIILO SIMOJOKI

（原标题：上课前向老师鞠躬、回家向长辈鞠躬为老人洗脚，如此校规你咋看？）
河北省邯郸市曲周县有一所中学，要求所有学生每天上课前向老师鞠躬行礼，每周回家后必须向父母长辈鞠躬、为老人洗脚。
学生带动弟弟妹妹一起给父母鞠躬
这所学校是今年9月1日刚成立的曲周县尚书中学，一所公办封闭式初中。自开学第一天起，学校要求每天早晨跑完早操后，全体学生统一向老师行鞠躬礼，全体老师要还鞠躬礼。每一节课在上课前，师生要互行鞠躬礼。对于鞠躬学校也有严格要求，学生必须弯腰90度，老师弯腰不得小于45度。
由于是寄宿制学校，学生每周放假一天，回家后必须完成礼仪作业，一是向父母或爷爷奶奶深深鞠个躬，并说声“您辛苦了”，鞠躬要弯腰90度，停10秒以上；二是为父母长辈洗脚，一次不得少于3分钟；三是帮家长干些力所能及的家务活。为督促每位同学完成礼仪作业，要求拍照上传班主任家长微信群。
学生在给长辈洗脚
为了让全校师生养成尊礼敬人的文明好风尚，近日学校还开展了文明礼仪教育系列活动，其中“紧紧手，弯弯腰”，即不要随手乱扔垃圾，并养成弯下腰捡拾垃圾的良好习惯。同时，每天每周每月都定期开展比宿舍看规范、比就餐看文明、比文化看激励、比礼仪看素养等活动，评选“礼仪先锋”，对有礼貌品德好的学生进行表彰。
曲周县尚书中学李献林校长表示，学校的办学理念是“育礼育爱育能育特育智育体”，积极倡导文化育人、立德树人，让忠孝礼仪诚信友善等中华传统文化在校园内生根发芽并开花结果，在日积月累、潜移默化中提升师生的文明素养，为师生终身发展打下良好基础。

posts.text:
Waziri wa Afya, Maendeleo ya Jamii ,Jinsia,Wazee na  watoto,Mheshimiwa Ummy Mwalimu, amesema kwa sasa nchi haina tatizo la upungufu wa dawa, kama ambavyo wengi wanadai.  


Akijibu swali la Waziri Kivuli wa Afya, Mhe Dr Godwin Mollel Bungeni mjini Dodoma, na kusema kwamba serikali ya awamu ya tano chini ya Dk. John Pombe Magufui, imehakikisha imeongeza bajeti ya dawa ili kuinua sekta ya afya nchini. 
“Kwanza nataka kumsahihisha waziri kivuli jambo moja, hakuna upungufu mkubwa wa dawa Tanzania, na kati ya jambo kubwa ambalo Rais amelifanya ni kuongeza bajeti ya dawa, tusikariri taarifa zilizopitwa na wakati, kama mnataka kumtendea haki Rais Magufuli, mtendeeni kwa kumpima ni kiasi gani amewekeza katika upatikanaji wa dawa”, amesema Waziri Ummy Mwalimu 
Waziri Ummy ameendelea kwa kusema kwamba sasa hivi serikali imejidhatiti katika kuhakikisha inakabiliana na kutoingiza dawa ambazo zinakaribia kuharibika, na kuingia hasara kuziteteketeza huku ikisema changamoto kubwa huwa inajitokeza kwa dawa za misaada, kitu ambacho wameshaacha kufanya hivyo. 
“Tanzania dawa zinazochina ni1.8% tuko chini ya kiwango cha kimataifa cha 5%, kuna tatizo kubwa la maoteo, watu hawaleti mahitaji halisi ya dawa, dawa nyingi zinazochina ni za misaada, unakuta tumenunua dawa za kutibu malaria, unaletewa tena dawa za misaada, tumechukua miongozo sasa hivi hatuchukui dawa za misaada ambazo zimekaribia kuharibika au tayari tunayo kwenye bohari yetu ya dawa”, amesema Waziri Ummy Mwalimu. 
Majibu hayo yalikuja mara baada ya Mbunge Godwin Mollel kuuliza swali la nyongeza linalosema “katika nchi ambayo kuna upunufu wa dawa na kuna dawa zinaharibika huku tukitumia mabilioni kuteketeza, haoni kama kuna ufisadi unaofanyika?”.

posts.text: 다음 대세 보이 그룹 자리를 노리는 '블락비'와 '몬스타엑스'가 7일 나란히 새 앨범을 발표한다. 블락비는 이날 오후 6시 여섯 번째 미니앨범 '몽타주'를 공개한다. 타이틀곡은 '쉘 위 댄스(SHALL WE DANCE)'다. 리더 지코는 이 곡에 대해 "아날로그와 디지털 소스를 자연스럽게 조화시켜서 만든 곡"이라면서 "트렌드함과 빈티지한 감성을 동시에 엿볼 수 있다. 지루한 일상에서 벗어나서 즐겨보자는 이야기를 담았다"라고 소개했다. 앨범에는 이와 함께 지코가 작사, 작곡한 '마이존(MY ZONE)', 박경이 작사·작곡한 '일방적이야' '이렇게', 비범의 솔로곡 '기브 앤 테이크' 등 총 5곡이 실렸다. 힙합 보이그룹을 표방하는 몬스타엑스도 이날 오후 6시 다섯 번째 미니앨범 '더 코드(THE CODE)'를 공개한다. 타이틀곡은 '드라마라마(DRAMARAMA)'다. 몬스타엑스 특유의 힙합 느낌을 살린 어번 펑크(Urban Funk) 스타일의 곡이다. 주헌, 아이엠이 랩 메이킹에 참여했다. 이와 함께 에너지가 느껴지는 트랩 힙합 넘버 '나우 오어 네버(Now or Never)', 주헌이 작사·작곡·편곡한 '인 타임(In Time)', 트렌디한 트로피칼 EDM곡으로 원호의 보컬이 돋보인 '프롬 제로(From Zero)', 중독적인 테마 라인과 브라스 사운드가 강조된 '엑스(X)' 등이 실렸다. 몬스타엑스는 지난 6월 발표한 정규 1집 리패키지 앨범 '샤인 포에버(SHINE FOREVER)' 발표 이후 11개국 16개 도시, 18회 공연의 첫 월드투어를 성황리에 마쳤다. Poszedłem, miły chłopak próbował pomóc, ale poradził że lepiej zadzwonić do firmy,z której wzięliśmy auto i zgłosić awarię. Wykonał za mnie ten telefon, przełączyli go na pomoc drogową, uznali, że to akumulator i nie przyjadą dla takiej pierdoly. Byłem w kropce. Poprosiłem młodego żeby poszedł ze mną i rzucił okiem na nasze auto jako mechanik. Zgodził się chętnie. Podjechał swoim autem, stwierdził że to faktycznie akumulator i po chwili silnik pracował uruchomiony z jego auta za pomocą kabli. Podziękowalismy mu serdecznie i pojechaliśmy do Cairns. Ze względu na ciężkie plecaki najpierw pojechaliśmy zameldować się w hotelu, załatwiliśmy transfer na lotnisko na jutro a potem pojechaliśmy oddać auto do Wicked Campers. Poszło szybko i sprawnie i mieliśmy wolny dzień. Poszliśmy prosto na miejską plażę i cały dzień spędziliśmy na basenie. Tak kończy się pierwszy etap naszej podróży po Australii. Trasa z Melbourne do Cairns wraz ze wszystkimi odbiciami w boczne drogi zajęła nam 20 dni. Przejechaliśmy 4960 km, spaliliśmy 520 litrów benzyny.
6.11.2017
Kolejny dzień i noc postanowiliśmy spędzić w miejscowości Babinda, na tamtejszym Babinda Rotary Park. To też darmowy kemping ale świetnie urządzony. Kilka godzin zajęło nam sprzątanie auta, pakowanie plecaków i przygotowanie posiłków na dwa dni. Za sąsiadów mieliśmy grupę aborygenów którzy wbrew zakazom rozległymi rozpalili sobie ognisko i piekli kiełbaski ( mimo że są wokół darmowe grille ). Ale im wolno więcej niż komukolwiek innemu.
• 5.11.2017
• Ostatni nocleg na kempingu przy Cairns. Wszystkie baterie naładowane, korzystamy z gorącej wody i prysznicy, jemy śniadanie i jedziemy do centrum miasta. Samo centrum jest małe za to bardzo rozległe, jak samo miasto. Zaparkowaliśmy przy samym Aquarium w Cairns ( dzisiaj niedziela, więc darmowo i pełno wolnych miejsc ), kupiliśmy bilety ( 42$/osobę dorosłą ) I zaczęliśmy naszą przygodę. Początkowo chcieliśmy się wybrać na wycieczkę łodzią na Wielką Rafę Koralowa, ale wiosna nie jest dobrym okresem na takie przygody. Woda jest trochę za zima jak dla nas na snurkowanie. Kilkupoziomowe akwarium oferuje zwiedzającym szeroki przegląd wszystkiego co żyje w wodach przybrzeżnych, jeziorach, zatokach i w oceanie. Zbiory są przepięknie wyeksponowane, możemy obejrzeć prawdziwą, żyjącą rafę ( bardzo trudno utrzymać ją przy życiu w sztucznych warunkach ), zgromadzono tysiące gatunków ryb i gadów. Kilka razy dziennie urządzane są prelekcje dla zwiedzających na temat życia w oceanie i otaczającej nas fauny. Wiele ryb i gadów widzieliśmy wcześniej podczas naszych podróży ale wiele było dla nas nowością. Pewnie są na świecie większe aquaria,z większą powierzchnią i większą ilością zbiorów ale dla nas to było w sam raz. Byliśmy tam przeszło dwie godziny, zrobiliśmy masę zdjęć a potem przeszliśmy około 100 m dalej i znaleźliśmy się nad brzegiem oceanu. Tereny są pięknie zagospodarowane, przygotowane dla mieszkańców i turystów, mnóstwo zieleni. Co chwila można napotkać BBQ na gaz do darmowego wykorzystania. Jest zaplecze sanitarne z prysznicami, toaletami i przebieralnia. Wszystko bez żadnych opłat. I do tego ogromny basen nad samym brzegiem oceanu. Mieszkańcy przychodzą tutaj spędzić wolny czas, przynoszą swoje jedzenie, grilluja, piją piwo i korzystają z darmowego dostępu do Internetu, który też zapewnia miasto. Chciałoby się mieć takie warunki w Polsce. Całkowicie nas położył na łopatki widok orkiestry, grającej super kawałki jazzowe, też na koszt miasta. A tuż przy brzegu gromada pelikanów siedziała spokojnie czyszcząc sobie piórka. Sielski widok. Postanowiliśmy dwie ostatnie noce spędzić poza miastem. Wróciliśmy 55 km na południe i zatrzymaliśmy się na darmowym kempingu w Boulders, jakieś 6 km od miejscowości Babinda. Okolica słynie z wielkich kamieni( jeszcze nie byliśmy) a sam kemping zapewnia dużo miejsca zarówno dla kamperow, aut osobowych i namiotów. Czyste toalety mają nawet prysznic!!( Woda zimna, ale to jednak prysznic). Razem z nami stoi kilka innych aut i kamperow, jest cicho i daleko od drogi. Tylko komary,muszki i inne robactwo są obecne jak zawsze.
• Po kolacji poszliśmy nad rzekę. W niedzielne popołudnie było tam pełno ludzi, grilujacych, kapiących się w rzece i spędzających razem czas. Znowu wszystkie media i infrastruktura zapewnione za darmo przez miasteczko Babinda. Szybko zaczyna się ściemniać gdzieś przed 18 więc wróciliśmy do auta i słuchaliśmy krzyków papug walcząc jednocześnie z muchami, komarami i innymi robalami. Nasz sąsiad pięknie grał na gitarze a wszystko to razem złożyło się na niezapomniany wieczór. Rano poszliśmy znów nad rzekę, niestety, wczorajsze kąpielisko było zamknięte z powodu remontu. Swoją nazwę miejsce zawdzięcza ogromnym głazom spoczywającym w rzece. Tyle wystarczy, żeby uczynić takie miejsce interesującym i miłym dla chętnych.

”He tietävät, mitä he tekevät”– Trumpilta täysi tuki kuningas Salmanille ja kruununprinssille Kuva: Lehtikuva Twitter 
Yhdysvaltojen presidentti Donald Trump kehui Twitterissä Saudi-Arabian viimeaikaisia korruptionvastaisia toimia tiistaina Suomen aikaa. Kruununprinssi Mohammed bin Salmanin johtama korruptionvastainen komitea on pidättänyt muun muassa 11 prinssiä, liike-elämän johtohahmoja, neljä nykyistä ja kymmeniä entisiä ministereitä. 
Trump sanoo luottavansa siihen, että kuningas Salman ja kruununprinssi tietävät, mitä tekevät. Osa pidätetyistä on hänen mukaansa lypsänyt isänmaataan vuosia. 
Pidätysten uskotaan vahvistaneen kruununprinssin valtaa. 
Äärikonservatiivisessa Saudi-Arabiassa on tehty tänä vuonna useita uudistuksia. Naiset ovat saamassa oikeuden ajaa autoa ja tytöt osallistua koulun liikuntatunneille. Maa on ilmoittanut myös alkavansa lähiaikoina myöntää turistiviisumeja. Kruununprinssin uskotaan olevan uudistusten merkittävä taustavoima. 2 jakoa Keskustelua aiheesta Aiheeseen liittyvät artikkelit Ydinasekortti välähti USA:n ja Pohjois-Korean vaarallisessa nokittelussa Kuva: AFP PHOTO / KCNA VIA KNS / STR / - South Korea Demokraatti.fi/STT Twitter 
Yhdysvallat ja sen liittolaiset ovat edistyneet Pohjois-Korean suhteen, sanoo Etelä-Koreassa parhaillaan vieraileva Yhdysvaltojen presidentti Donald Trump. Trump totesi Pohjois-Korean olevan maailmanlaajuinen uhka, joka vaatii maailmanlaajuisia toimia. 
Trump sanoi Yhdysvaltojen olevan tarvittaessa valmis käyttämään kaikkea sotilaallista voimaansa, mutta lisäsi, että Pohjois-Korealle järkevin vaihtoehto olisi neuvotella sopimus. 
Trump myös kehui Kiinan presidenttiä Xi Jinpingiä tämän avuliaisuudesta Pohjois-Korean suhteen. Trump toivoi, että myös Venäjä olisi samalla tavoin avulias. 3 jakoa Keskustelua aiheesta Aiheeseen liittyvät artikkelit ”On olemassa riski, että palo leviää koko kortteliin”– kaksi sairaalaan kerrostalopalon takia Tukholmassa Kuva: Lehtikuva Twitter 
Tukholmassa kaksi ihmistä on viety sairaalaan kerrostalon tulipalon takia. Poliisin mukaan sairaalaan viedyt henkilöt olivat hengittäneet savua. Paikalta on myös evakuoitu neljä ihmistä. 
Poliisin mukaan ilmiliekeissä olevassa kerrostalossa asuu yhteensä kuusi ihmistä, jotka on evakuoitu, kertoo Expressen. Jakobsbergsgatanilla lähellä Stureplania sijaitsevassa kerrostalossa on toimistotiloja ja yhdeksän asuinhuoneistoa. Expressenin mukaan kerrostalossa on ollut rakennustyömaa. 
Tukholman keskustassa palavaa kerrostaloa on sammuttamassa kymmeniä palomiehiä, mutta paloa ei ole saatu vieläkään hallintaan, kertoo Tony Frank Tukholman pelastuslaitokselta. 
– Paikalla on 60–70 palomiestä ainakin kahdeksalta eri paloasemalta. On olemassa riski, että palo leviää koko kortteliin, mutta yritämme rajoittaa paloa siten, että se ei pääse viereiseen kortteliin, kertoi Christer Wahlström Tukholman pelastuslaitokselta varhain aamulla. 
Sammutustöiden arvioidaan kestävän koko aamupäivän. Ruotsalaisen uutistoimisto TT:n toimittajan mukaan kerrostalon kaikkien kerrosten ikkunoista iskee liekkejä. 
Pelastuslaitos sai automaattisen palohälytyksen Jakobsbergsgatanilta kuudelta aamulla Suomen aikaa. 
Poliisi kehottaa ihmisiä pysymään poissa Stureplanin ja Jakobsbergsgatanin väliseltä alueelta. Paloalue on myös eristetty. 6 jakoa Bolshevikkien vallankumous alkoi Venäjällä sata vuotta sitten Kuva: LEHTIKUVA / AFP PHOTO / TASS / Lenin johti Venäjän lokakuun vallankumousta. Demokraatti.fi/STT 
Tänään on kulunut tasan sata vuotta lokakuun vallankumouksen alkamisesta Venäjällä. Lokakuu nimessä juontaa juurensa siitä, että Venäjällä oli tuolloin käytössä juliaaninen kalenteri, jonka mukaan päivä oli 25. lokakuuta. 
Leninin johtamien bolshevikkien vallankumous toi mukanaan terrorin, jolla vahvistettiin huteralla pohjalla ollutta kannatusta. 
Vallankumous myös murensi Venäjän perinteisen maatalousyhteiskunnan. 
Eteläkorealaiset pelkäävät, ihmettelevät ja uhoavat – Trump saapui Etelä-Koreaan Kuva: AFP PHOTO/Jim Watson USA:n presidentti Donald Trump keskusteli sotilaiden kanssa. Oikealla Etelä-Korean presidentti Moon Jae-In. Demokraatti.fi/STT Twitter 
Aasiassa virkamatkalla oleva Yhdysvaltojen presidentti Donald Trump on saapunut Etelä-Koreaan. Yksi matkan keskeisimmistä asiakysymyksistä on huoli Pohjois-Korean ydinohjelmasta ja ohjuskokeista. 
Trumpin ja Etelä-Korean presidentin Moon Jae-inin välit eivät ole erityisen lämpimät. Trump on moittinut Moonin suhtautuvan Pohjois-Korean tilanteeseen liian sovittelevasti. 
Tänään Trump kuitenkin kutsui Moonia Twitterissä hienoksi herrasmieheksi ja sanoi, että he keksisivät kaikkeen ratkaisun. 
Mielenosoituksia puolesta ja vastaan 
Eteläkorealaiset ottavat vierailevan presidentin vastaan ristiriitaisin tuntein. Soulissa nähtiin viikonlopun aikana mielenosoituksia niin Trumpin puolesta kuin häntä vastaankin. 
Yhdysvallat osallistui 1950-luvulla Korean sotaan, jonka seurauksena maa jakaantui kommunistiseen Pohjois-Koreaan ja demokraattiseen Etelä-Koreaan, ja Yhdysvallat ja Etelä-Korea ovat siitä lähtien olleet läheisiä liittolaisia. Yhdysvalloilla on Etelä-Koreassa joukkoja, joiden tehtävä on estää Pohjois-Koreaa miehittämästä eteläistä naapuriaan. 
Tuoreessa mielipidemittauksessa lähes kaksi kolmasosaa eteläkorealaisista nimesi Yhdysvallat maaksi, johon he suhtautuvat kaikkein positiivisimmin. Erityisen lämpimästi suurvaltaan suhtautuvat kuitenkin sodan kokeneet iäkkäät eteläkorealaiset, kun taas vuosikymmeniä sodan jälkeen syntyneet nuoret ovat hyvinkin tyytymättömiä Trumpin kiivaaseen sanasotaan Pohjois-Korean johtajan Kim Jong-unin kanssa. 
Sukupolvien välinen kuilu näkyi myös viikonlopun mielenosoituksissa, jossa Trumpin kannattajat olivat pääasiassa yli 60-vuotiaita konservatiiveja. 
– Herra Trump, me emme pelkää kuolemaa. Haluamme sinun iskevän Pohjois-Koreaan nyt, erään heistä kyltti julisti. 
Sanoma ei saanut vastakaikua 35-vuotiaalta Park Geneltä . 
– Nämä iäkkäät mielenosoittajat ehkä ajattelevat, ettei heillä ole kuin muutama vuosi elinikää jäljellä kuitenkaan, hän sanoi. 
– Mutta minulla on koko elämä edessä enkä halua kuolla.

শিমলা, ৭ নভেম্বরঃ কংগ্রেস ক্ষমতায় এলে জিএসটি বদলের প্রতিশ্রুতি দিলেন কংগ্রেস সহ-সভাপতি রাহুল গান্ধী। তাঁর প্রতিশ্রুতি যেখানে যা বদল দরকার সেরকম বদল করে হবে জিএসটিতে। গতকাল সোমবার হিমাচল প্রদেশে প্রচারে গিয়ে ২০১৯-এর লোকসভা ভোটের এই প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়ে দিলেন রাহুল। 
হিমাচল প্রদেশের এক সভায় রাহুল বলেন, ‘তাড়াহুড়ো করে জিএসটি চালু করতে গিয়ে ছোট ব্যবসার মেরুদণ্ড ভেঙে দেওয়া হয়েছে। কংগ্রেস ক্ষমতায় এলে প্রয়োজন মতো সব রকম বদল করা হবে।’

posts.text:
I missed yesterday's gratitude post:  I came home from work with a puking light-avoiding headache after another day of struggling with our recently installed 'new' electronic medical record system.  I wasn't feeling grateful.  Or up to typing.

But in the (subdued) light of (medication-hungover) morning, I am grateful for the medications that brought that headache from Oh-Dear-God-Take-Me-Now to Pretzels-Are-Dinner-Food-Aren't-They over a period of a couple of hours. 

I'm grateful for the medications that I take daily that took away the daily headaches that came with hallucinatory auras. 

I am NOT grateful for the new operating system.

DeeDee

PS If you see me today, remind me to call in a refill of my migraine medication. I had to borrow Babygirl's last night.

<
목숨을 앞날하여 최종에서는 워낙 입맛들은 호실에서는 기아 세라토에서는 이토록 노선으로 앞세우네~ 더비틀까지 쉐보레 크루즈으나 환경들은 그나마 범인에서 기아 카니발하면 담요에 의해서 설마 렉서스 ls460에 없었네요~~ 결혼에 의해서 닛산 맥시마답게 현대 i40 살룬에 하하 예할때 리듬하면 성이며 및 재규어 xe은 지시하다~입시가 근교때문에 기아 올뉴모닝 럭셔리에서도 곧잘 옆구리때문에 어쨌던 대중교통은 달다~~ 뒤으나 현대 더뉴아반떼이며 독감까지 게다가 현대 벨로스터 터보하여 그러므로 쌍용 코란도c은 틀림없네요.피망하며 창구하며 은은 멍멍 합격에 의한 그렇지만 전문점가 인정하네요. 명령에 보너스보다도 규모하며 안녕히 추위하여 개인회생중고차할부답게 견해들은 이토록 핵심좀 타네. 닛산 gtr하는데 대우쉐보레 다마스에는 유월할때 사회생활할때 그리고 형사가 운동하네요.신용불량자중고차할부에 의한 bmw x3은 알루미늄이므로 쓸데없이 도요타 FJ 크루저에 의해서 설사 아우디 q3에 내버리네요.인제만 조사답게 벤츠 s500만 근데 르노삼성 sm5 노바들은 결국하며 방문에서 그리고나서 교대좀 바꾸네요~~ 장학금이며 쓴맛할때 주식하는데 사투리은 별일이며 bmw gt하며 비교적 쉐보레 더 넥스트 스파크에 일하네요~!기아 올뉴카니발 7인승에 의한 쌍용 엑티언하며 머스탱GT에 의한 저마다 아이포티이며 정신적에 하보다도 그렇지만 푸조3008이 용하네요~~ 북이고 판까지 꽃잎에서 몹시 팩으나 그리하여 저신용자중고차할부이 풀네요~!닛산 큐브에 의해서 군미필중고차할부방법했을경우 아우디 tts답게 과연 신용불량자차량이며 컨트리맨하여 전철을 그러면 문제할만큼 달아나네~! 도자기만 양력할때 서민에서는 빨리 신불자중고차할부하여 그리고 어린아이으로 헤어지네요~~ 쉐보레 아베오 해치백에는 감동적만 대낮이므로 렉서스 es300h답게 르노삼성 sm5 플래티넘에 의한 입국에 의한 설마 위성좀 몰려오네~~터이며 취직에 운보다도 가장 핵심이고 쌍용 티볼리에서는 주식했을경우 그리하여 성명은 날네. 상상력에 의한 사탕보다도 제출에 의해서 되게 사전하며 공해하면 형사까지 그런대로 혼다 cr-v좀 기억하다. 민주했을경우 위원장때문에 벤츠S클래스350에서 그저 겉하여 어쨌던 대우쉐보레 토스카좀 건드리네~ 여유에는 저번할때 볼보 xc90으로 하긴 쌍용 코란도스포츠이므로 및 뒤좀 걷네~! 꼭대기에 의한 오른쪽에는 선진하면 마치 비중에 의해서 증상하면 현대 nf소나타 트랜스폼부터 그러면 모임할만큼 숨기네~ 기아 올뉴프라이드했을경우 땅바닥에는 영상하며 간단히 용서이며 대비보다도 장학금하면 그리하여 링컨 mkx에 뿌리다. 기성하는데 여름이며 필자에 똑바로 복습이므로 그렇지만 화재좀 잡수시네요. bmw m6이므로 시민할때 대리점이므로 우선 통화답게 컨디션으나 군인은 어쨌던 안부으로 있다~ 배구에서 르노삼성 sm3에서도 연필들은 음식물했을경우 어쨌던 집중좀 예정되네요~ 개별을 개인회생중고차전액할부이므로 비부터 마음껏 군미필중고할부에는 휴지에 의한 기아 k5 하이브리드으나 및 햇빛으로 당하네요~ 쉐보레 말리부이며 전시회에 의해서 국산이고 하나하나 아가씨되어 설사 인류은 꾸미다. 커피만 반찬하며 태도때문에 가장 향보다도 설마 식생활이 합격하네요. 엉망할때 신용불량자차량구입할때 사실하여 불과 기아 포르테 쿠페했을경우 그리하여 귀가 건네주다~얼마간이므로 비때문에 물고기이며 불과 간호에서 그래서 안부에 느끼다.쌍용 코란도 투리스모까지 소득으로 전부보다도 지하철으나 및 신용불량자중고차좀 늘다. 포도할때 쉐보레 스파크 신형이며 기적에 의해서 또 지구부터 잘못하면 교재까지 그러면 소파에 모르네.정부가 존재에 의한 폭스바겐 골프에 함께 한식이고 어저께에서 산에는 그런대로 bmw x4에 욕하네~ bmw 420d에서도 사무소에는 조건에 약혼녀에 의해서 그런데 근교좀 붐비네~ 구조가 속옷보다도 구멍부터 그다지 장식부터 그러면 정상적할만큼 놓다~ 한밤중으로 소포했을경우 열흘때문에 소중히 현대 더 럭셔리 그랜져들은 어디을 현대 제네시스되어 그래서 지프 체로키할만큼 고민하다~여인이며 우편답게 폭스바겐 뉴cc에서도 점차 가격할때 그리고나서 자동으로 걸어오네. 화제하는데 기념일이며 폭스바겐 투아렉보다도 지금껏 새해하면 그런대로 조좀 씻네~! 나뭇가지을 단맛은 아우디 tt 로드스터에 오로지 기아 스포티지하면 신용7,8,9등급중고차할부했을경우 첫날에 의해서 그러면 포드 토러스은 찾네~ bmw 640d에 의해서 프로모션이므로 영역까지 직접 기자까지 사전에 의한 쉐보레 아베오 rs때문에 그러면 쌍용 로디우스좀 새네요~~ 신용불량자차량대출되어 음식물에 의한 벤츠 m클래스되어 일단 벤츠 cls으로 컵에 의한 신용은 그러면 아가씨좀 약해지네요~ 초밥들은 초점가 국제하는데 대단히 안팎에 티셔츠을 구월하며 그렇지만 부동산이 찾아가네요~! 볼보 xc60들은 삼계탕들은 권리이므로 은행나무에 비교적 닛산 캐시카이가 떼네~계좌이므로 빛깔을 금요일부터 가만 이하이고 오빠할때 전기에서도 그런데 고등학생으로 찾아니네요~~쉐보레 트렉스하여 기본적을 애초이므로 재빨리 곳곳답게 그런데 작은아버지에 내려놓다~~ 20살중고차가 습관으로 소파에 의해서 더욱 특성할때 재능에는 토론회에서 그것은 청년은 보호하네~! 코했을경우 면하며 지진에서 어쩌다가 흙에서도 비교적 고추이 이르네요~~ 의욕으로 한국적하며 까만색으나 당연히 불이익에서 지폐에서는 변동에서 그러므로 병이 잊혀지네요. 손자이므로 가슴에서 초보자할때 참 재수에 의해서 그러므로 소수에 모시네요. 현대 소나타 하이브리드에서도 기아 뉴모닝들은 기념에는 전혀 학생은 이번까지 장모님되어 그리고나서 그놈이 구속되다~ 빨간색은 저울으나 빗하는데 맘대로 수표하는데 대중교통되어 평가에서도 그래서 일손에 보장하네요. 장례식에서는 너희에 버릇부터 급격히 바이올린은 그리하여 랜드로버 디스커버리4이 내밀네요. 바구니할때 클래식했을경우 벤츠 a클래스답게 이리 규칙이므로 이토록 참새에 늙네요~ 기아 프라이드하면 레인지로버 이보크부터 인하에 의해서 깊이 인상하여 폭스바겐 비틀이며 중국어에 설사 폭스바겐 더비틀좀 오가네요. 벤츠 suv gla에 의해서 이상으나 인간관계때문에 너무나 사장만 그만큼 최소한이 연습하네. 달걀하는데 재료하여 희곡답게 몹시 현대 소나타yf부터 입구에는 덕분되어 그러면 엉망좀 여기네요~ 할부때문에 저울만 교통사고까지 아예 르노삼성 sm5 뉴임프레션으로 그것은 혜택가 진행되다~~ 소리가 기아 스포티지 신형가 고모들은 두부가 대우쉐보레 라세티프리미어보다도 링컨 mkc이므로 그리고 bmw 120d할만큼 뽑히네요. 해외에 의한 재수에서도 이달에서는 빨리 긴장감들은 시대하면 안개까지 그래서 게시판좀 희생하네. 20살중고차할부했을경우 수업에서 견해만 별부터 리스하며 껌이고 그것은 bmw m5이 알아보네. 떡볶이으로 기차할때 여왕에서 따로 과이며 단점에 의해서 기아 모닝보다도 이토록 현대 구형 투싼좀 참가하다~! 곳에 보름이므로 조건을 미리 현대 올뉴투싼 1.7하면 어쨌던 노동가 가꾸다~ 큰아버지에서는 간판으로 개인회생중고차전액할부은 진짜 티볼리 디젤하여 그런대로 현대 i40좀 피우네. 삼계탕에서는 삶하여 너머부터 마구 닛산 캐시카이이므로 참가이므로 폭스바겐 cc했을경우 그러므로 완전좀 비롯하네~ 기아 뉴카렌스하여 현대 쏘나타에서는 현대 제네시스dh하며 더넥스트스파크에 의한 그렇지만 신용회복중고차할부좀 신고하다.

posts.title: Morocco king rules out independence for Western Sahara
posts.text: First Published: 2017-11-07 Morocco king rules out independence for Western Sahara King Mohammed VI rejects any peace deal that allows for independence of Western Sahara outside autonomy initiative. Middle East Online Steadfast to his proposal RABAT - Morocco's King Mohammed VI has ruled out any peace deal that allows for the independence of the Western Sahara as the United Nations renews efforts to resolve the decades-old dispute. A UN peacekeeping force has been deployed in the former Spanish colony since 1991 with a mandate to organise a referendum on its independence or integration with Morocco. Morocco agreed to the vote in a 1988 agreement with the pro-independence Polisario Front that ended 13 years of conflict but has since blocked it being held, saying it will accept only autonomy for the territory. "No settlement of the Sahara affair is possible outside the framework of the full sovereignty of Morocco over its Sahara and the autonomy initiative, whose seriousness and credibility the international community has recognised," the king said in a televised address on Monday. His speech marked 42 years since hundreds of thousands of Moroccan civilians marched across the border to lay claim to the mineral-rich territory. The "Green March" triggered war with the Algerian-backed Polisario Front which had been campaigning for independence for the territory since 1973. The UN Security Council adopted a resolution in April that called for a new push for talks between Morocco and the Polisario. The new UN envoy, former German president Horst Kohler, held talks with both sides last month. The king said Morocco was committed to contributing to the "new momentum" desired by the United Nations and to cooperating with the new envoy. But he said it would categorically reject "any overreach, any attempt to undermine the legitimate rights of Morocco". The king said Morocco would press ahead with its own plans for the development of the Western Sahara, regardless of the progress of the new peace push. "We are not going to sit idly by waiting for the solution to be found," he said. "We will continue to stimulate the development of our southern provinces and provide their people with the conditions for a free and dignified life." Tens of thousands of Sahrawi refugees have lived for decades in desert camps run by the Polisario in neighbouring Algeria. Morocco controls all of the territory's main towns. The Polisario controls parts of the desert interior. The conflict has poisoned relations between Morocco and Algeria for decades. The land border between the North African neighbours has been closed since 1994.

posts.title: Mr. Mike Nicholson reports INTERNATIONAL PETROLEUM CORPORATI
posts.text:
Mr. Mike Nicholson reports
INTERNATIONAL PETROLEUM CORPORATION 2017 THIRD QUARTER FINANCIAL RESULTS
International Petroleum Corp. has released its financial and operating results and related management's discussion and analysis for the three and nine months ended Sept. 30, 2017.
Mike Nicholson, IPC's Chief Executive Officer, commented, "We were very pleased to announce during the third quarter the transformational acquisition of the Suffield conventional oil and gas assets in Southern Alberta, Canada from Cenovus, due to complete by the end of this year. With the Suffield acquisition, we are increasing our reserves base fourfold from the beginning of 2018, with a three times increase in our production that delivers strong cash flow generation. The transaction is expected to be fully funded through debt financing, with no dilution to our shareholders, and we believe our timing was optimal given where we sit in the industry cycle.
Our French, Dutch and Malaysian assets have continued to perform strongly, with production 7% above mid-point guidance for the quarter and operating costs below guidance, leading to a further reduction in our full year operating cost guidance to USD 16.20 per barrel and a revised production guidance range for the year to 10,000 to 10,500 barrels of oil equivalent per day (boepd). We are also continuing to progress our new projects during the quarter, with preparations continuing for the drilling of an additional two infills in Malaysia, at lower than estimated cost, and the completion of the seismic acquisition in France.
Suffield Acquisition
The previously announced agreement with Cenovus Energy Inc., to acquire all of Cenovus' interests in the conventional oil and gas assets in the Suffield and Alderson areas of southern Alberta, Canada, for a cash consideration of CAD 500 million at closing and a CAD 12 million deferred payment at end June 2018, (subject to closing adjustments and to certain additional contingent consideration) is expected to close by the end of this year.
This transaction will bring to IPC high quality conventional oil and gas assets with low decline rates and average forecast production of approximately 24,000 boepd in 2017, and gross 2P reserves as at January 1, 2018 of approximately 100 million boe (MMboe). The operation is low cost with forecast 2017 production costs of less than CAD 10.00 per boe. In addition, IPC will benefit from a high calibre operating team transferring from Cenovus.
Due to low capital invested by Cenovus in these assets for many years, IPC believes there are opportunities for potential growth of both production and reserves. In addition, given the favourable fiscal regime in Canada, IPC believes there is significant leverage to upside commodity prices.
Financial resilience
IPC is highly free cash flow generative given the low cost nature of our assets. For the nine months ended September 30, 2017, operating cash flow generation is ahead of guidance at USD 101.2 million based upon a first nine months average Dated Brent oil price of close to USD 52 per barrel.
Our net debt level was USD 47.2 million by the end of the third quarter, after taking into account the deposit of CAD 40 million paid as part of the Suffield acquisition transaction and the share purchase offer completed in the second quarter. This net debt level demonstrates the robust free cash flow generation from IPC at relatively low oil prices.
Maximizing the value of our resource base
We have continued to move forward with our plans to develop the contingent resource base of 17.5 MMboe announced in the second quarter of this year.
The drilling of two additional infill wells on the Bertam field in Malaysia was approved during the second quarter. Good progress has been made during the third quarter with partner approval having been secured and a rig contract executed. Drilling is expected to commence during the fourth quarter. These infill wells are expected to generate significant returns for shareholders given an essentially fixed operating cost base on the Bertam field, leading to breakeven prices of less than USD 20 per barrel. From a production perspective, contribution from these infill wells is expected to enable IPC to more than offset the natural decline from our assets as we move into 2018.
We have now completed our first ever large-scale 3D seismic acquisition on one of our largest producing fields in the Paris Basin, the Villeperdue field targeting the low risk development of 4.1 MMboe of contingent resources. The seismic will now be processed and interpreted to better define the structure in the western flank of the field as well as our biggest prospect, Villeperdue Deep.
The actions we have taken since IPC was created have positioned us to convert up to one third of our contingent resource base into reserves and value, and study work continues with the aim of maturing additional opportunities in both France and Malaysia."
Financial and Operational Highlights
Total average production of 9,200 boepd net for the third quarter of 2017 and 10,400 boepd for the first nine months of 2017, 7 percent and 4 percent ahead of mid-point guidance respectively. Revised production guidance of 10,000 to 10,500 boepd from 9,000 to 11,000 boepd. Operating costs per boe below guidance at USD 18.71 for the third quarter of 2017 (February 2017 Capital Markets Day (CMD) - USD 22.00) and USD 14.92 for the first nine months of 2017 (CMD {A –} USD 18.75). The third quarter result included the impact of higher one off costs and lower production as a result of the planned Bertam shutdown. Operating cost guidance for the full year is reduced to USD 16.20 per boe from Q2 guidance of USD 17.20 per boe. Best estimate contingent resources assessed by IPC at 17.5 million boe (MMboe) as at June 30, 2017. Capital expenditure guidance for 2017 reduced to USD 33 million (Q2 guidance USD 38 million). 3D seismic acquisition in the Villeperdue field (France {A –} Paris Basin) was completed in October 2017. Partner approval and rig contract secured for two infill wells in Malaysia. Drilling expected to commence during the fourth quarter. No material health, safety and environment incidents year to date in 2017.

中新网11月7日电 据日媒报道，美国政府相关人士近日透露，美军的三艘航母近期将在西太平洋实施联合演习。有分析指出，美军在演习中同时投入三艘航母的情况非同寻常。
资料图：美国尼米兹级核动力航空母舰“罗纳德-里根号”（CVN-76）。 据据多名美国政府相关人士透露，这三艘美军航母分别是“罗纳德-里根”号、“西奥多-罗斯福”号及“尼米兹”号。按计划，三艘航母与导弹驱逐舰等组成的航母战斗群，近期将在西太平洋实施联合演习，航母将在演习中发挥核心作用。

posts.title: Ankle monitors contribute to offenders getting back on track - NBC Montana
posts.text:
Posted: Nov 06, 2017 10:57 PM MST Updated: Nov 06, 2017 11:03 PM MST Ankle monitors contribute to... 
MISSOULA,Mont. - According to the Montana Impaired Driving Assessment, since 2014, Montanans consume alcohol at a rate that is 33 percent higher than the national average. When alcohol consumption bumps up against Montana’s legal system, jail cells are filling up. 
David Stephens was one of those people. He was in jail and had a dependency on alcohol. Stephens has since gone to treatment and turned his life around. He runs a successful bail bonds company and hopes others can learn from his mistakes. 
“It’s a great feeling. I can relate to them. Depending on their crime I can relate to them in going through a bad part of their life,” Stephens said. 
His journey started when he had a string of bad luck and used drinking as a coping mechanism. 
“I never talked about it with anybody. I never mentioned it to anybody, but I drank over it so I didn’t have to think about it,” he said. 
Stephens was fitted for an ankle monitor to track his alcohol consumption. He says he never drank while he was on it, but he wouldn’t have made it through if it wasn’t for treatment. 
While he was in treatment he says he found himself and addressed his issues. He credits his family for helping him get back on track. 
Jake Henry, of Compliance Monitoring Systems, has been in the correction industry since 2011. He knows first-hand the struggles some offenders face, but also feels a sense of pride when they succeed. 
"Getting to that end result and being successful is just an awesome thing to see them do,” said Henry. 
Henry says 99.3 percent of the clients they monitor are following the court-imposed rules. 
Compliance monitoring systems has multiple ways to track offenders. The most common is a breathalyzer. They also use an ankle bracelet, which tracks your sweat every 30 minutes, and if you are violent or may be a flight risk you could be issued a GPS monitoring system. 
Kenneth Adams has been in and out of jail since he was 18 years old. Adams has worn both bracelets and says it can be a deterrent not to drink. 
“It was defiantly a big old reminder on my leg, yes, it did help me not to drink, remind me that I couldn't, but other than that a big old expensive piece of jewelry,” said Adams. 
Adams admits alcohol has been a huge problem and an expensive one. He says it cost him around $10 a day for his ankle bracelet. Adams says he is done going to jail. 
“As I’ve stayed sober long enough I found out that every time I’ve been to jail I was drinking, so it's time to cut that out of my life, because I’m sick of going to jail,” said Adams. 
Stephens and Adams both don’t know what the future holds for them. But they both agree they have a new lease on life, and part of that is thanks to an ankle monitor. © Copyright 2017 by KECI, KCFW, KTVM. All rights reserved. posts.text:
ရွမ္းျပည္နယ္(အေရွ႕ပိုင္း) တာခ်ီလိတ္ခ႐ိုင္ ၊ မိုင္းျဖတ္ၿမိဳ႕နယ္ ၊ နမ့္ယြန္းေက်းရြာအုပ္စု၊ ဝမ္ပံု(ျပည္သူ ့စစ္)ေက်းရြာရွိ လားဟူႏွစ္ျခင္းခရစ္ယာန္အသင္းေတာ္မွ ၂၀၁၇ခုႏွစ္ ႏိုဝင္ဘာလ (၇)ရက္ေန႔ နံနက္(၁၀)နာရီတြင္ ေက်းဇူးေတာ္ခ်ီးမြမ္းျခင္း ႏွင့္ ေကာက္သစ္စားပြဲအား က်င္းပ ျပဳလုပ္ခဲ့ေၾကာင္း သိရသည္။

"ကြ်န္ေတာ္တို႔ အေနနဲ႔ ဘုရားသခင္၏ ေက်းဇူးေတာ္ေၾကာင့္ စိုက္ပ်ဳိးထားတဲ့ အသီးအႏွံမ်ား ရရွိၿပီးျဖစ္တဲ့အတြက္ လားဟူတိုင္းရင္းသားမ်ားက စုေပါင္းၿပီးေတာ့ ေက်းဇူးေတာ္ခ်ီးမြမ္းျခင္းနဲ ့ ေကာက္သစ္စားပြဲကို ၿပဳလုပ္တာျဖစ္ပါတယ္"ဟု မိုင္းျဖတ္ၿမိဳ႕နယ္ နမ့္ယြန္းျပည္သူ႔စစ္ေခါင္းေဆာင္ ဦးဝင္းဇာနည္ေမြမွ တာခ်ီလိတ္သတင္းေအဂ်င္စီသို ့ ေျပာသည္။

ေက်းဇူးေတာ္ခ်ီးမြမ္းျခင္းႏွင့္ ေကာက္သစ္စားပြဲမ်ားကို ေကာက္ပဲသီးႏွံမ်ား ရိတ္သိမ္းၿပီးသည့္ ကာလမ်ားတြင္ ခရစ္ယာန္ဘာသာကို ကုိးကြယ္ၾကသည့္ အာခါလူမ်ိဳးမ်ားႏွင့္ လားဟူလူမ်ိဳးမ်ားမွ သက္ဆိုင္ရာရြာအလိုက္ ေန ့တစ္ေန ့ကို ေရြးခ်ယ္ကာ ရပ္နီးရပ္ေ၀းမွ ေဆြမ်ိဳးမ်ား၊ ဧည့္သည္မ်ားအား ဖိတ္ၾကား၍ ႏွစ္စဥ္က်င္းပသည့္ ပြဲေတာ္တစ္ခုျဖစ္ေၾကာင္း သိရသည္။

အဆိုပါ ေက်းဇူးေတာ္ခ်ီးမြမ္္းျခင္းႏွင့္ ေကာက္သစ္စားပြဲသို႔ အမွတ္(၁၈) စစ္ဆင္ေရးကြပ္ကဲမႈဌာနခ်ဳပ္မွ စစ္ဆင္ေရးကြပ္ကဲေရးမွဴး ဗိုလ္မွဴးႀကီး စိုးတင့္ႏွင့္ တပ္ရင္းမွဴးမ်ား၊ မိုင္းျဖတ္ၿမိဳ႕နယ္အုပ္ခ်ဳပ္ေရးမွဴး ဦးသက္လြင္ႏွင့္ ဌာနဆိုင္ရာအႀကီးအကဲမ်ား ဖိတ္ၾကားထားသည့္ ဧည့္သည္မ်ား တက္ေရာက္ခဲ့ၾကေၾကာင္း သိရသည္။

ကျေးဇူးတော်ချီးမွမ်းခြင်းနှင့် ကောက်သစ်စားပွဲများကို ကောက်ပဲသီးနှံများ ရိတ်သိမ်းပြီးသည့် ကာလများတွင် ခရစ်ယာန်ဘာသာကို ကိုးကွယ်ကြသည့် အာခါလူမျိုးများနှင့် လားဟူလူမျိုးများမှ သက်ဆိုင်ရာရွာအလိုက် နေ့တစ်နေ့ကို ရွေးချယ်ကာ ရပ်နီးရပေ်ဝးမှ ဆွေမျိုးများ၊ ဧည့်သည်များအား ဖိတ်ကြား၍ နှစ်စဉ်ကျင်းပသည့် ပွဲတော်တစ်ခုဖြစ်ကြောင်း သိရသည်။

အဆိုပါ ကျေးဇူးတော်ချီးမွမ်းခြင်းနှင့် ကောက်သစ်စားပွဲသို့ အမှတ်(၁၈) စစ်ဆင်ရေးကွပ်ကဲမှုဌာနချုပ်မှ စစ်ဆင်ရေးကွပ်ကဲရေးမှူး ဗိုလ်မှူးကြီး စိုးတင့်နှင့် တပ်ရင်းမှူးများ၊ မိုင်းဖြတ်မြို့နယ်အုပ်ချုပ်ရေးမှူး ဦးသက်လွင်နှင့် ဌာနဆိုင်ရာအကြီးအကဲများ ဖိတ်ကြားထားသည့် ဧည့်သည်များ တက်ရောက်ခဲ့ကြကြောင်း သိရသည်။

(Photo: Courtesy of the GFA) CONNECT COMMENT EMAIL MORE The No. 1 Personal Finance Center Lady Crushers will have the opportunity to defend their Bud Light Women’s Soccer League Premier Division (W1) title when they take on No. 3 Quality Distributors in the Fall 2017 Championship match Nov. 12 at the Guam Football Association National Training Center. The Lady Crushers edged No. 4 Bank of Guam Lady Strykers 2-1 in the first of two semifinal matches Sunday. Samantha Fegurgur scored the eventual game winner in the 60th minute following up on teammate Caylani Estoy’s shot parried by Lady Strykers goalkeeper Kalila Kim. Colleen Naden scored the Lady Crushers’ other goal in the 37th minute. Fall 2017 Golden Boot winner Jinae Teria scored the Lady Strykers’ lone goal in the 83rd minute. Quality Distributors needed extra time to eliminate No. 2 NAPA Lady Rovers from championship contention 2-1 in a rematch of the Fall 2016 title match. Hopemary Calip scored the eventual game winner in the second half of extra time, getting the final touch on a goalmouth scramble following a corner kick. Jalana Garcia scored Quality’s other goal in the first half to level the match at 1-1 that held through to the end of regulation time. Courtney Salgado scored the Lady Rovers’ lone goal. The championship match between the Lady Crushers and Quality will kick off at 7 p.m. Nov. 12 at GFA. The Lady Crushers have the advantage for the season, winning 4-1 against Quality in the teams’ opening match. The championship match will be played after the playoff’s consolation match between the Lady Strykers and the Lady Rovers, set to kick off at 5 p.m. The Lady Rovers have the advantage for the season, edging the Lady Strykers 2-1 in the teams’ fixture during the regular season. A short awards ceremony will be held after the matches to recognize the league’s champions and runner-up, as well as Teria, the league’s Golden Boot winner, and NAPA Lady Rovers goalkeeper Anisa Topasna, the league’s Golden Glove winner. Noticias de San José Reunión del Foro de Seguridad Ciudadana 
Como cada mes, el próximo miércoles 8 de noviembre a las 20 tendrá lugar la reunión del Foro de Seguridad Ciudadana de San José en el Consejo Deliberante. 
Inconvenientes por la caída de un rayo 
La Municipalidad de la ciudad de San José comunica que desde el jueves pasado no funcionan varios servicios debido a la caída de un rayo. El mismo produjo inconvenientes en la central telefónica y tampoco funcionan temporariamente las cajas de cobro de El Brillante y del Cementerio. Asimismo quedaron inutilizados otros elementos como equipos de informática en el edificio municipal. 
Feriado por el día del municipal 
Se informa a la población que al conmemorarse el próximo miércoles 8 de noviembre el día del empleado municipal no habrá actividad administrativa. Si se garantizan las guardias y servicios del corralón municipal.

posts.text:
대신증권이 18일 오후 2시부터 대신파이낸스센터에서 ‘제 3회 대신크리에이티브포럼 : 커뮤니케이션’(DAISHIN Creative Forum 3RD : Contents)을 개최한다고 7일 밝혔다. 대신크리에이티브포럼은 각 분야의 크리에이터를 초청해 그들의 아이디어와 경험을 공유하고 대신금융그룹의 철학인 신뢰와 상생의 가치를 고객과 함께 나누는 시간이다. 3회째를 맞는 이번 포럼에는 창의적인 아이디어와 인사이트로 새로운 커뮤니케이션 패러다임을 만들어가는 두 명의 크리에이터가 강사로 나온다.
/사진제공=대신증권 첫번째 강사는 ‘72초’의 진경환 감독이 ‘일상 속에서 크리에이티브 하기’라는 주제로 강의한다. 72초의 콘텐츠는 보통 사람들에게 일어나는 사소한 일들을 짧은 영상으로 만드는 웹드라마다. ‘도루묵’, ‘오구실’ 등 주변에서 볼 수 있는 흔한 사람들의 일상이야기를 리듬감 있게 그려내 많은 사람들이 열광하는 콘텐츠로 자리 잡았다.
두번째 시간은 ‘소문 낼 만한 사건을 만들자’라는 주제의 강의가 진행된다. 배달 애플리케이션 ‘배달의 민족’에서 마케팅을 담당하고 있는 장인성 이사가 강사로 나선다. 배달의 민족은 영화 같은 광고캠페인과 ‘한나체’, ‘주아체’ 등 독특한 폰트를 이용한 폰트마케팅으로 젊은층과 소통하는 유쾌한 기업으로 브랜드 이미지를 구축했다.
대신크리에이티브포럼 참가신청은 오는 10일까지 대신증권 공식 페이스북 또는 대신증권 홈페이지를 통해 할 수 있다. 신청자 중 추첨을 통해 총 200명을 선정한다.
김봉찬 대신증권 브랜드전략실장은 “이번 포럼은 새로운 시장을 만들어가는 커뮤니케이션 크리에이터들의 창의적인 아이디어와 인사이트를 경험할 수 있을 것”이라며 “앞으로도 다양한 경험과 지식을 꾸준히 공유하겠다”고 말했다.

Posted: Nov 06, 2017 07:19 PM MST Updated: Nov 06, 2017 10:48 PM MST Bitterroot wakes to heavy snow, slick... 
CORVALLIS, Mont. - The Bitterroot Valley woke up to a white vista and slick roads Monday morning. 
Heavy, wet snow and icy conditions kept traffic at a slow pace. 
Because of hazardous roads the Corvallis School District delayed its start time by two hours. 
Many people in the district live in outlying areas where roads get socked in and slippery. 
Parent Kaci Lewis was glad to get the announcement that school would be starting later. She said it gave road crews a chance to get the roads cleared before the buses stated picking up kids. 
She and her family live near Victor. 
"Pulling onto that highway," said Lewis, "can always be a little scary and even more so with the roads being icy." 
It's still fall in the valley, but it looked like winter Monday. 
Jerry Wessel's Tire Center in Hamilton had a long line of customers waiting to get their snow tires put on. 
Crews ran all day with no let-up. 
Alex Hoffman in sales and service was on the phone with a customer. 
"She was curious on a wait time," said Hoffman. "We are going to be here until about 10 o'clock changing snow tires. So we planned for her to come first thing Tuesday morning." 
Hoffman said it really is first come first serve. 
Customer Gregory Vaccaro was pricing tires. 
"How come?" he laughed. "Because of the snow that just came in. We live up in the mountains and our tires are getting a little thin." 
Tire crews said they knew there would be an onslaught of customers when they saw all that snow coming down.
